data.name: smartOperationCheckBoxLabel.ToolTip
data.value: This option is important only for dealing with multiple artists/composers per track. Every byte of the source tag (including the service characters that identify the roles of the artists) will be preserved if this option is unchecked; however, this may be useful only if the source and destination tags are the same.
